# Asset Management Module ‚Äî Product Brainstorm & Plan

> Strategic plan for a comprehensive Asset Management module that elevates the app from cashflow tracking to true wealth management.
> Status: **Brainstorm + plan only ‚Äî no execution requested.**

---

## Context

### Why this module is needed

The app today is a **cashflow tracker** ‚Äî it answers *"where did my money go?"* It does not answer *"how much am I worth?"*, *"is my wealth growing?"*, or *"is my portfolio balanced?"*

Concretely, the current state has:
- **No proper Account/Wallet entity** ‚Äî `wallet` is a free-text string on transactions ([apps/api/src/PersonalFinance.Domain/Entities/Transaction.cs](apps/api/src/PersonalFinance.Domain/Entities/Transaction.cs))
- **No proper Bank/Institution entity** ‚Äî bank codes are hardcoded across [TransactionsController.cs:64-68](apps/api/src/PersonalFinance.Api/Controllers/TransactionsController.cs#L64-L68), [Program.cs:85-93](apps/api/src/PersonalFinance.Api/Program.cs#L85-L93), and [BankIdentifier.cs](apps/api/src/PersonalFinance.Infrastructure/Parsers/BankIdentifier.cs)
- **No balance tracking** ‚Äî `bank_running_balance` exists on transactions but is used purely as a deduplication tie-breaker (PF-090), not as a balance ledger
- **No snapshots over time** ‚Äî there is no historical view of what any account/asset was worth at a point in time
- **Custom wallets are stored in `localStorage`** ‚Äî see [AccountsTab.tsx](apps/frontend/src/pages/cashflow/AccountsTab.tsx) (`pf_custom_wallets`), so they are device-local and unreliable
- **Settings already has a disabled placeholder** for "Banks & Accounts" in [SettingsLayout.tsx](apps/frontend/src/pages/settings/SettingsLayout.tsx) ‚Äî the gap is acknowledged

### What "professional-grade" means for this user

This is a **single-user power-tool app** for an Indonesian user managing 5 banks across IDR/USD with mixed cash, investment, and real-asset exposure. Professional-grade here means:
- **Bloomberg-Terminal density** for the user, not a Mint-style consumer dashboard
- **Honest tracking** ‚Äî no fake auto-sync; manual entry is fine when it's the truthful path
- **Time-series first** ‚Äî every value has a date; net worth is a chart not a number
- **Multi-currency native** ‚Äî IDR base, but FX-aware
- **Composable with cashflow** ‚Äî a transaction debiting BCA reduces BCA's balance; the two modules are not separate islands

